    <Variables>
      <Variable name="dT0250" type="finiteStates" role="chance">
        <Comment><![CDATA[<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    This reflects the change in T level for the electrode(s) responsible for 
    the coding of 250 Hz. Up stands for 1 unit up, in the developer's mind 
    this is up by 5 current units.
  </body>
</html>]]></Comment>
        <Coordinates x="310" y="161" />
        <AdditionalProperties>
          <Property name="Relevance" value="7.0" />
        </AdditionalProperties>
        <Precision>0.01</Precision>
        <States>
          <State name="down" />
          <State name="st.quo" />
          <State name="up" />
        </States>
      </Variable>
      <Variable name="Nerve_0250_Soft" type="finiteStates" role="chance">
        <Comment><![CDATA[<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    This reflects the change in significant neural activity in the tonotopical 
    region responsible for 250 Hz, when stimulated with intensities around 
    threshold. Up stands for 1 unit up, in the developer's mind this is a 
    level that should be noticeable for 95% of patients.
  </body>
</html>]]></Comment>
