      <Variable name="T0250" type="finiteStates" role="chance">
        <Comment><![CDATA[<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0">
      This is the absolute T-level. It is known at the beginning of the 
      fitting and should always be entered.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0">
      In the developer's mind Low stands for under 42, High for over 68.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>]]></Comment>
